(Super !)</i>

43
00:03:55,174 --> 00:03:58,047
<i>Et te voir rayonner
(Continue !)</i>

44
00:03:58,048 --> 00:04:01,315
<i>Voir tes lèvres sourire</i>

45
00:04:01,316 --> 00:04:04,388
